      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta check out this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s looking flawless and drives like a total dream. No scratches, no weird noises\u2014just pure, polished perfection. I\u2019m really looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
