    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant. This specimen boasts factory-spec subframe reinforcement and a meticulously maintained Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The double VANOS system has been recently overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the entire 8,000 RPM powerband. Performance is further anchored by the factory limited-slip differential and a suspension geometry that remains true to its original N\u00fcrburgring-tuned specifications. With zero panel gaps and a chassis free of oxidation, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical integrity.",
