      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the tactile surfaces remain matte and fresh. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a documented service history and a powertrain that delivers smooth, effortless performance. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, investment-grade example that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
